{"tid":241110,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"居屋癲升 沙田愉田苑呎價逼1.3萬創新高","createTime":"2017-05-13T01:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T03:52:44.000Z","uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61ca761fbbe75abb71afb97e092174d4bfff07ce","tid":241110,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T01:28:26.000Z","msg":"大公網5月12日訊(記者林惠芳) 二手交投氣氛持續向好，樓價節節上揚，部分買家轉投居屋市場入市，沙田愉田苑一個2房單位，新近獲用家以呎價近1.3萬元連地價承接，創屋苑呎價歷史新高。<br />\n<br />\n　　中原地產首席分區營業經理陳迪豪表示，沙田居屋愉田苑G座(愉群閣)高層03室，實用面積434方呎，建築面積531方呎，以555萬元連地價易手，實用呎價12788元，創屋苑呎價歷史新高。<br />\n<br />\n　　陳迪豪指，新買家為用家，見屋苑少有放盤，即把握機會入市自住。原業主於2013年以318萬元買入單位，當時單位已補地價，持貨約4年，是次轉手帳面獲利237萬元離場，單位升值約74.5%。"},{"pid":"f56ecfc319ee789dee73683d791c6a917ca0c3b5","tid":241110,"uid":56462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T01:36:59.000Z","msg":"比多少少對面欣廷軒都買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f4699247f5faacdd69640fd0e875aae1980da3","tid":241110,"uid":96854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T03:52:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比多少少對面欣廷軒都買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSorry唔得...<br />\n<br />\n沙田欣廷軒呎價升破1.6萬元。消息指2座高層E室兩房戶，實用面積396方呎，因有租客居住，買家在「冇樓睇」下以645萬元承接，呎價16,288元，創屋苑呎價歷史新高。原業主2012年10月以435萬元買入單位，不足5年升值近五成，賬面獲利210萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56685639&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170512\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56685639%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170512&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN2xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=87deb9f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56685639%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170512&h=4586c5ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56685639&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170512</a>"}]}